<p>Kefir even has a similar load as a normal two-year-old youngster.</p>

<p>She added: 'He has another propensity: around evening time he gets a kick out of the chance to hop on me and rest. At the point when he was a little cat, it didn't cause me any bother.</p>

<p>'However, presently he has become enormous and weighty, and, obviously, it is hard to rest like that.</p>

<p>'Kefir is presently one year and ten months old and weighs 28lbs.</p>

<p>'He is as yet thought to be a cat. Maine Coons grow up to 3-4 years. Consequently, I figure it ought to turn out to be significantly bigger.'</p>

